  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the clay tajine over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional 1 minute.",
    "Add the lamb cubes and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the mustard seeds and miso paste.",
    "Add the mustard-miso mixture to the clay tajine and stir to combine.",
    "Add the chicken broth, molasses, and chopped parsley to the clay tajine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 2 hours.",
    "Remove the clay tajine from the heat and let it rest for 10 minutes before serving."
